             was indicted for <rs id="t18191201-65-off392" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18191201-65-off392" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191201-65-off392" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18191201-65-cd393" type="crimeDate">27th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-65-off392 t18191201-65-cd393"></join>, thirty-seven yards of flannel, value 20 s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18191201-65-victim806" type="victimName">
                           George 
                           Minton
                        <interp inst="t18191201-65-victim806" type="surname" value="Minton"></interp>
